Class MavenBootstrapTaglet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ball.tools.javadoc.AbstractTaglet
      • ball.tools.javadoc.MavenBootstrapTaglet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatedTaglet, JavadocHTMLTemplates, HTMLTemplates, XalanConstants, XMLConstants, XMLServices, com.sun.tools.doclets.Taglet

    public abstract class MavenBootstrapTaglet
extends AbstractTaglet
    AbstractTaglet whose register(Map) method loads all Taglets specified through a ServiceLoader. Designed to be specified as <tagletClass/> in a Maven pom.xml.
